<h3>POST /api/ragpicker/line_items/add</h3>
<div>
  add a line item
</div>
<b>Resource URL </b>
<div>
http://ragpickers.herokuapp.com/api/ragpicker/line_items/add
</div>
<b>sample request</b>
<div>
  curl --data "line_item[category_id]=1&line_item[pick_up_id]=6&line_item[quantity]=0.2&token=login_token" "http://ragpickers.herokuapp.com/api/ragpicker/line_items/add"
</div>
